From 60212a3766be5b04ab8a7757620dba32909dd0b4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 11:24:14 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 5/5] Apply learnability principles across the app

- Adopt lucide-react for all icons (remove custom inline icon set)
- Define design tokens in tailwind.config (brand color scale, radius
  control/card/panel, card shadows) and route components through token
  classes (.card/.panel/.btn/.input/.chip) in index.css
- Explicit hover/active/focus-visible states on every interactive element
  (buttons, links, sidebar rows, icon buttons, rail icons)
- Specific form validation messages (what's wrong + how to fix) shown
  inline per field with error styling, focus first error + summary toast
- Clear label + placeholder on every form field (htmlFor/id wired up)
- Conventional SaaS layout retained (rail + sidebar + content + modal)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01JJ2ALpPXcgcr9CfdzcsDU4
